sequenceDiagram
    participant main
    participant process
    participant Heap
    
    main->>Heap: Create vec![1,2,3,4,5]
    Note over main: numbers owns the Vec
    main->>process: Move numbers to data
    Note over main: numbers now invalid
    Note over process: data owns the Vec
    process->>process: Use data
    process->>Heap: Drop data, free memory
